    {%- comment -%}
      Removed 2026-04-26 PM: lazysizes.js (~25 KB JS, 1,680 ms total
      CPU per Lighthouse). Theme code no longer depends on it after
      today's data-src + data-bgset migrations to native loading="lazy".
